id: pm-7t04
title: Add pm init checks for AGENTS/CLAUDE pm workflow guidance
description: "Teach pm init to detect whether AGENTS.md and/or CLAUDE.md include core pm command/workflow guidance, ask before adding missing guidance, persist declined prompts, and expose an explicit init option to add the guidance later."
type: Feature
status: open
priority: 1
tags[5]: agent-ux,bootstrap,docs,init,pm-cli
created_at: "2026-05-17T08:58:01.020Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-17T09:03:03.303Z"
author: codex-agent
acceptance_criteria: pm init detects missing core pm guidance in AGENTS.md and/or CLAUDE.md; TTY init asks before modifying files; approval writes idempotent marked guidance; decline persists project state so future init runs do not ask; explicit pm init option can add guidance later; non-interactive runs do not block; settings/schema/contracts/help/docs/tests cover the behavior.
parent: pm-rnpb
